{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"hasAccess": false, "showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "6696579c623b9ed1d4637466", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 210, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "MOG", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76cfc52ffa3c944600e0"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eb9e"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "66965789b31faf98fda8fef9", "title": "JEE Advanced 2024 (Paper 1)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "An infinitely long wire, located on the $z$-axis, carries a current $I$ along the $+z$-direction and produces the magnetic field $\\vec{B}$. The magnitude of the line integral $\\int \\vec{B} \\cdot \\overrightarrow{d l}$ along a straight line from the point $(-\\sqrt{3} a, a, 0)$ to $(a, a, 0)$ is given by\n[ $\\mu_0$ is the magnetic permeability of free space.]", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "cbdd2", "text": "$7 \\mu_0 I / 24$", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "XzL3f", "text": "$7 \\mu_0 I / 12$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "sOFxL", "text": "$\\mu_0 I / 8$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "bVPPb", "text": "$\\mu_0 I / 6$", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_advanced/dOwQMQIMqWc3qSYk7vRYoO8D2tUqLEGHE9AM4qGhLbU.original.fullsize.png\">\n$\\begin{aligned} & \\Rightarrow|\\overrightarrow{\\mathrm{d} \\ell}|=\\mathrm{rd} \\theta \\\\ & \\Rightarrow|\\overrightarrow{\\mathrm{B}}|=\\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{I}}{2 \\pi \\mathrm{r}} \\\\ & \\Rightarrow \\int \\overrightarrow{\\mathrm{B}} \\cdot \\overrightarrow{\\mathrm{d} \\ell}=\\int|\\overrightarrow{\\mathrm{B}}||\\overrightarrow{\\mathrm{d} \\ell}| \\cos 0^{\\circ} \\\\ & =\\int\\left(\\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{I}}{2 \\pi \\mathrm{r}}\\right) \\times(\\operatorname{rd} \\theta) \\\\ & =\\int_{\\theta_1}^{\\theta_2} \\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{I}}{2 \\pi} \\mathrm{d} \\theta=\\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{I}}{2 \\pi}\\left[\\theta_2-\\left(-\\theta_1\\right)\\right]\\end{aligned}$\n[ $\\theta_1$ is anticlockwise hence taken negative]\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_advanced/v4ARfWjdth5qjuv2qokm1juok7gPsOSGKck2oWYOK4A.original.fullsize.png\">\n$\\begin{aligned} & \\Rightarrow \\tan \\theta_1=\\frac{\\mathrm{a} \\sqrt{3}}{\\mathrm{a}}=\\sqrt{3} \\\\ & \\theta_1=\\frac{\\pi}{3} \\\\ & \\Rightarrow \\tan \\theta_2=\\frac{\\mathrm{a}}{\\mathrm{a}}=1 \\\\ & \\theta_2=\\frac{\\pi}{4} \\\\ & \\Rightarrow \\int \\mathrm{B} \\cdot \\mathrm{d} \\ell=\\frac{\\mu_0 \\mathrm{I}}{2 \\pi}\\left[\\frac{\\pi}{3}+\\frac{\\pi}{4}\\right] \\\\ & =\\frac{7 \\mu_0 \\mathrm{I}}{24} \\\\ & \\Rightarrow \\text { Ans. Option (1) }\\end{aligned}$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": {"videoId": "c2c755d0b99b4f16b63469181a58eacb", "provider": "vdocipher", "thumbnailLight": "https://d1z78r8i505acl.cloudfront.net/poster/4uO4XYtucJGQj.480.jpeg", "thumbnailDark": "https://d1z78r8i505acl.cloudfront.net/poster/4uO4XYtucJGQj.480.jpeg", "premiumModules": [{"premiumModuleId": "6628114842d540dfcb148ecb", "isFree": false}, {"premiumModuleId": "64c7e8e829737784b294e469", "isFree": false}, {"premiumModuleId": "6788cc0b2dbc1ecacabb7026", "isFree": false}], "description": "JEE Advanced (All PYQs from 2023 - 2013)"}, "masterId": "MOGJAPYQ28236166", "isRemoved": false, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87